  <h2 id="checklist">How to try it safely (quick checklist)</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Turn on Kill Switch and IPv6 blocking in the app.</li>
    <li>Select a Double VPN pair (entry close to you, exit close to the service area).</li>
    <li>Connect and run both a speed test and a DNS/IP leak test.</li>
    <li>Use a hardened browser profile (separate profile/containers) to limit cookie carry-over.</li>
    <li>Disable Double VPN for streaming/gaming or when you need max speed.</li>
  </ol>

